Tai5-tang hu7-kun7 sou2 ui7 Pyuma (彪馬) chok8 u7 hun-soaN3 ti7  8 e5 hiuN-sia7 teh khia7-khi2.  Phou2-thong teh kong2 ‘Poeh-sia7’ chiu7 si7 teh chi2 Pyuma chok8 e5 i3-su3 teh kong2. m7-ku2 goan5-lai5 Pyuma si7 chi2-khi2 Lam5-ong5 hit chok8 na7-tiaN7, i2-goa7 iau2 u7 Ti-pun2, Sia7-ma2-kan, Li7-ka, Thai3-peng5-chhoan, Siong7 Pin5-nng5, Ha7 Pin5-nng5 kap Chhou-lok8 (Leng5-ke3-meh8 chai7-lai7 ) chiah e5 hiuN-sia7.  Sou2-i2 tu5-khi3 Lam5-ong5 i2-goa7, ki5-thaN e5 hiuN-sia7 e5 lang5 khah bo5 ai3 hou7 lang5 kio3-choe3 Pyuma.  Chong2 kong2, in tai7-ke khah ai3 eng7 ‘Poeh-sia7’ chit e5 beng5-chheng, sui-bong2 si7 an2-ni, eng7 ‘Pyuma’ lai5 tai7-piau2 Poeh-sia7 ia7 m7-si7 put-kai.  In-ui7 cha2 tui3 Pyuma chit chhoan u7 chhut in Poeh-sia7 e5 ong5, kio3-choe3 Pi-lam5 ong5, teh ti7-li2 Pi-lam5 hiong hu7-kun7 Poeh-sia7 chok8.  Hian7-chai7 tang Tai5-oan5 e5 san-toe7, piN5-toe7 san-pau ke3-kiong7 u7 Ami, Bunun, Drukai, Paiwan, Pyuma, Taroko, kap Yami chiah e5 7 chok8.  Ki5-tiong chin cha2 chiu7 chhut gau5 lang5 khah choe7 e5, chiu7-si7 Pyuma chok8.  Tui3 in e5 lai7-bin7 i2-kip8 in e5 hou7-e3 u7 chhut Seng2 cheng3-hu2 ui2-oan5, i-seng, koan7-tiuN2, gi7-oan5, keng2-chhat sou2-tiuN2, kok-hau7 hau7-tiuN2, im-gak8-ka chin-choe7 e5 le7.  An2-ni Pyuma  chok8 khiok si7 iu-siu3 e5 bin5-chok8, sui-bong2 in e5 lang5-giah8 hap8-oa2 bo5 tat8 chit8 ban7 lang5, chong2-si7 cha2-cheng5 in u7 Ami chok8 choe3 in e5 lou5-le7  e5 su2-sit8. Cha2  Pyuma chok8 bat cheng-hok8  Ami chok8, ti3-kau3 Ami chok8 siok8 in ti7-li2, choe3 in e5 lou5-le7 . Sou2-i2 kau3 hian7-chai7 Ami chok8 chheng Pyuma chok8 choe3 Aldaalda (i3-su3 si7 tui3-tek8 alda e5 hok8-sou3). 
Ti7 ke3-khi3 Pyuma chok8 sui-bong2 u7 bin5-chok8-siong7 put-chi2 thang khoa-khau2 e5 hui-hong5 e5 lek8-su2.   Chong2-si7 in e5 leng5-seng3-siong7 si7 li7  Ki-tok e5 kiu3-un chin hng7.  
Tui3 10 goa7 ni5 cheng5, ki3-chia2 chiu7 kam2-kak iau2 u7 tiau5-goa7 kho2-lin5 e5 iuN5, bo5 lai5 in2-chhoa7 in boe7 an-sim, (in-ui7 pun2-lang5 e5 kang-chok toa7-pou7-hun7 si7 tui3 Ami chok8 e5 thoan5-kau3), chiu7 tui3 Lam5-ong5 khai si2, au7 lai5 kau3 Li7-ka, Ti-pun2 teng2 hong-bin7 choe3 kang, chong2-si7 hau7-ko2 chin ban7.  Sui-bong2 ke3-khi3 ia7 siong5-siong5 chio Tan5 Chin3-chong Koan7-tiuN2 tau3 eng3-oan7 choe3-tin7 khi3 in e5 hiuN-sia7, a2-si7 ti7 koan7-tiuN2 e5 kong-koan2 li7-iong7 tek8-piat8 e5 chu7-hoe7 tui3 in thoan5 hok-im, in e5 hoan2-eng3 chin ban7. 
Li7-ka e5 hiuN-sia7 ia7 bat ti7 chin ku2 e5 tiong-kan, mui2 le2-pai3 e5 pai3 si3 am3 ong2-hoe5 che7 kha-tah8-chhia nng7 tiam2 goa7 cheng soa3-chiap choe3 kang, tit tioh8 Loe7-te7-hoe7 e5 Ki2 Kui3-peng5 Kou-niu5 (Miss Giebel) kap Ai Kou-niu5 (Miss Ashby) teng2 choe3-tin7 pang-bang5, hau7-ko2 ia7 si7 chin iu2-han7.  In-ui7 Thian-chu2-kau3 lai5 Tai5-tang hong-bin7 khai-si2 choe3 kang, choe7-choe7 lang5 ui7-tioh8 in teh pun e5 kiu3-che3-phin2 lai5 siu7 be5-hek8. Chit8 peng5 eng7 but8-chit; chit8 peng5 eng7 Seng3-keng; kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, si7 I e5 Seng3 Sin5 u7 choe3 kang ; hou7 hiah e5 thau5-nau2 pi2-kau3-tek kan2-tan e5  Pyuma e5 tong5-pau, na2 tit8-tit8 khun3 chhiN2  khi2-lai5.  Tek8-piat8 choe3-kun7 chit nng7 ni5 lai5, u7 ke-thiN kui2-na7 e5 put-chi2 iu2-lek8 e5 chi2-to7 kai-kip e5 lang5, tui3 in kong2 khi2 Seng3-keng e5 chin-li2-Siong7-te3 e5  Oe7  hou7 in thiaN e5 si5, in keng3-jian5 koat-sim jin7 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok choe3 in e5 Kiu3-chu2.  In put-chi2 u7 An-tek-liat, Hui-lek8 kap Po2-lo5 e5 cheng-sin5, hian7-chai7 iau2 put-chi2 phah-piaN3 ui7 Chu2 choe3 kian3-cheng3, teh in2-chhoa7 kok sia7 iu2-lek8 e5 thau5-lang5 lai5 kui Chu2.  
Choe3-kun7 ia7 u7 tit8-tioh8 chit8 e5 tui3 chin cha2 chiu7 teh in2-chhoa7 e5 iu2-lek8-chia2 Ma2 Ti3-le2 koat-sim saN-kap ti7 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5 hong7-hian3 koat-sim e5 ki5-to2.  I si7 tiam3 Chhou-lok8, koh si7 Pyuma chok8 i2-goa7 ki5-thaN kok chok8 sou2 kong-jin7 e5 san-toe7 e5 chong2 thau5-bak8.  Kun7-lai5 sin-the2 khah lam2, ia7 u7 khi3 Hoa-lian5 M.C.C. PiN7-iN7 jip8-iN7 ti7-liau5. Si3 geh8 be2 tng Oan2-tong kui Chu2 sou2 phai3 lai5 e5 Rev.H.B.Williams ti7 Tai5-tang hong-bin7 ka7 lan2 hiap8-chou7 thoan5-kau3 e5 ki5-kan tiong, pun2-lang5 u7 chhoa7 i khi3 tham3 Ma2 Ti3-le2.  Williams Bok8-su eng7 Chu2 e5 to7-li2 khoan3-bian2 i, i ia7 kap i saN kap ki5-to2.  I piau2 si7 goan7-i3 chiap-lap8 Ia5-sou choe3 Kiu3-chu2, ia7 hoaN-hi2 tau3 kou2-bu2 hiah e5 siong5-siong5 lai5 chhe7 i e5 san-toe7 tai7-piau2 lai5 tui-kiu5 Chu2 e5 chin-li2.  In-ui7 i si7 choe3 hu7-kin7 kok chok8 e5 ho2 e5 kou3-bun7.  Kong-hok8 au7 siu7 cheng3-hu2 ko-kip koaN-oan5 in2-kian3 e5 san-toe7 tai7-piau2 chiu7-si7 i.
Hian7-chai7 Poeh-sia7 chok8 tu5 Chhou-lok8, Ti-pun2 i2-goa7, long2 u7 khi2 le2-pai3-tng5. Thoan5-kau3-chia2 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7 pit-giap8 e5 u7 nng7 e5 teh choe3 kang, i2-goa7 iau2 u7 nng7 e5 chi3-goan7 e5 soan7-to7-su teh chi2-to7. Kang-chok jin5-oan5 iau2 chin khiam3, goan2 u7 chin7-liong7 teh chai-poe5 hoaN-hi2 tau3 heng-khi2 hok-im e5 kang-lang5, hou7 in hu7-chek chi2-to7 bu5 bok8 e5 kau3- hoe7. Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, Li7-ka kau3-hoe7 e5 Tan5 Siong5-lim5 TiuN2-lo2 tui3 jip8 sin3 liau2-au7, tau3 phun-chau2 kok sia7, kek8-lek8 teh in2-chhoa7 hit toe7-hng e5 iu2-lek8-chia2, ia7 u7 teh chou-chit Se-pou7 kau3-hoe7 hong2-bun7-thoan5, hou7 hiah e5 iu2-lek8 e5 tai7-piau2 tham3 lan2 choe3 a-hiaN e5 kau3-hoe7 kap ki5-thaN e5 ki-koan, chiu7-si7 piN7-iN7, hak8-hau7 teng2, liau2-au7 ia7 teh ki5-thai7 oe7 thang tit-tioh8 chham-ka ti7 te2-ki5 e5 chin3-siu-pan siu7 hun3, hou7 in tit-tioh8 siok8 leng5 e5 chai-bat, liau2-au7 thang ti7 in e5 chok8 tiong ui7 Chu2 hoat kng.  ChhiaN2 khoaN3 Po3 e5 hiaN-chi2, ui7-tioh8 chiah e5 Poeh-sia7 chok8 e5 leng5-hun5 e5 tit-kiu3 kap chiah e5 chi2-to7-chia2 ki5-to2, ng3-bang7 Chu2 e5 Sin5 beh toa7-toa7 choe3 kang ti7 in e5 tiong-kan. Sou2-i2 “ Lan2 chiah e5 oe7 e5 lang5 eng3-kai tioh8 tam-tai3 boe7 e5 lang5 e5 loan2-jiok8” ( Lo5-ma2 15:1,2).  ChhiaN2 tai7-ke ui7-tioh8 Tai5-oan5 San-toe7 kok chok8 tiong, te7 it ban7 siN e5 ke2-chi2 Pyuma chok8 e5 tit-kiu3 lai5 koan-sim.
